properties.Name: AtmServiceType
properties.Description:
A specific type of service or function that may be offered at a specific ATM machine such as:

- Deposits
- Loan payments
- Cash
- Bill payment 
- Stamp purchase
- Mortgage loan payment
- Individual account access
- Printing of statements
- Transfer of funds

Columns.Name: AtmServiceTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ATM Service Type.

Columns.Name: AtmServiceTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of an ATM Service Type.

Columns.Name: AtmServiceTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an ATM Service Type.
